data.description: Beautiful home convenient to USA, Spring Hill, I-65, shopping, parks, and more. A brand new roof was installed in January of 2022! You must see this 3 bedroom 1 bathroom, move-in ready home. The home has nice sized bedrooms, a large den with a fireplace, and an extra nook that is great for a desk or sitting area. Outside, the fenced back yard features a carport, and good storage. The property is located in a quiet neighborhood with minimal traffic, this area provides lots of convenience. This wonderful home will not be available for long. Schedule a showing today! The listing broker makes no representation of square footage accuracy Buyer to verify.
